{"word":"Πέτρος","slug":"Πέτρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Πέτρος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> unclear] <b>Peter, Rockman,</b> surname of one whose name, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> cited, heads the lists of the apostles <b><a href='B:470 10:2'>Mt 10:2</a>; <a href='B:480 3:16'>Mk 3:16</a>; <a href='B:490 6:14'>Lk 6:14</a>; <a href='B:510 1:13'>Ac 1:13</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> referred to as Simon <b><a href='B:470 4:18'>Mt 4:18</a>; <a href='B:470 16:16'>16:16</a>; <a href='B:490 5:8'>Lk 5:8</a>; <a href='B:490 6:14'>6:14</a>; <a href='B:500 1:42'>J 1:42</a>; <a href='B:500 18:10'>18:10</a>; <a href='B:500 21:15'>21:15</a>; <a href='B:510 10:5'>Ac 10:5</a>; <a href='B:510 11:13'>11:13</a>; <a href='B:680 1:1'>2 Pt 1:1</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πέτρα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πετρώδης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}